class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">暗黃(件衫)</span></span>達哥好醒, 擺明係暗黃都賺到藍紅資本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為香港忍辱負重推足一年JOB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於得到國家賞識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/13/68LFgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F13%2F68LFgO.png&h=d4475a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/13/o0tpb9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F13%2Fo0tpb9.png&h=8bb8941c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/13/WgHuO6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F13%2FWgHuO6.png&h=f0e67c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n達哥大腦實驗<br />\n平時達哥打機經常做出異於常人舉動<br />\n到底達哥係腦殘，定係天賦異稟？<br />\n達哥的腦年齡究竟是多少？立即去片<br />\n本節目由富途牛牛贊助播出<br />\n#富途牛牛 #eDDA入金 #ETF<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_1dFlPM08bY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_1dFlPM08bY&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=9779ff25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_1dFlPM08bY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日，元朗發生「元朗西鐵站恐怖襲擊」事件。翌日潛水多時的達哥終於上水，在表達對元朗事件的憤慨之餘，同時更嚴斥一直指罵他的網民，直言「你估我一直比人鬧緊唔出聲好過癮呀？」，又稱<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「我推咗幾多Job我係咪又要出post話你知啊？」</span></span>，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">質疑如果大眾需要的是「咩都攞出嚟做show先叫有做野」的KOL，自己確實並非如此。</span></span>他又表示「我出post香港問題就即刻解決我義無反顧，你寫好畀我直出都得！問題係我亂出post只係幫需要出嚟被問責嘅人spin個風向去我度咋，你明唔X明啊！」不過大批網民通通不買帳，更直指達哥用詞全部「戴晒頭盔」，有網民更將其字眼與其他支持反送中的YouTuber聲明比較「你睇達狗寫『差佬』，人哋寫『黑警』，高下立見。」 網民認為他以發爛渣形式在Facebook發文，指責自己的舊支持者，又單打其他網絡紅人，令舊支持者進一步死心，更有忠實粉絲怒燒印有達哥Q版肖像的遊戲卡，以示對達哥的徹底失望。<br />\n<br />\n富途表示，騰訊作為戰略投資者，與富途在多個合作領域上有互惠互利的關係，其合作是基於雙方共同對技術與創新的價值觀。在2018年12月，旗下於中國實體運營的公司深圳富途（Shenzhen Futu）與深圳騰訊計算機系統公司（Shenzhen Tencent Computer System）簽訂戰略合作框架協議。騰訊將通過其在線平台與富途在流量、內容與雲端上合作。<br />\n<br />\n上市前，公司創辦人兼董事長李華持股51.7%，為最大股東；而騰訊則為第二大股東，持股為38.2%；經緯創投則持6.1%，為第三大股東；而第四大股東為紅杉資本，持4%股權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/e5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1/encode/full\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegapx.dcard.tw%2Fv1%2Fimages%2Fe5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1%2Fencode%2Ffull&h=00366422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69ca4178edaec6bdff572cf33f5cc43141a915cd","tid":2106322,"uid":24133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d07d0e192ab3f1bb321227d8b8515918635d0e2","tid":2106322,"uid":205043,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04cc4244409c905758f5dabe118417ca9dc5f72d","tid":2106322,"uid":229502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d51929df254901a0d3a476c9e108895e24b87746","tid":2106322,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"達朝復活了！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1982641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1982641</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇下復出第一日班達粉幾撚興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我入去鳩up兩句就出晒黎護主，而家班柒粉潛撚晒落地核<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:19:05.000Z","msg":"我中立嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我指出事實啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"達哥由一萬人收視插水到得返十分一<br />\n<br />\n我都係講事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"今朝凌晨ubugsoft開live都重有千幾人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達朝永垂不朽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac